Hugh Wakefield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_Wakefield 0 Hugh Wakefield (10 November 1888 – 5 December 1971) was an English film actor, who played supporting roles. He was often seen wearing a monocle. Wakefield was born in Wanstead, Essex. He also had a distinguished stage career, which began at the age of 11. City of Song (1931) was his first film. He died 5 December 1971 in London aged 83. Hugh_Wakefield ( 10_November_1888 – 5_December_1971 ) was an_English_film_actor , who played_supporting roles . He was_often_seen_wearing a_monocle .
